# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the jacksonville jaguars need salary cap room and the kansas city chiefs need a quarterback .
# ::alignments
(a / and
      :op1 (n / need-01
            :ARG0 (t / team
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Jaguars")
                  :location (c / city
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Jacksonville")))
            :ARG1 (r / room
                  :mod (c2 / cap-01
                        :ARG1 (s / salary))))
      :op2 (n4 / need-01
            :ARG0 (p / person
                  :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 (c3 / city
                              :location (s2 / state
                                    :name (n5 / name
                                          :op1 "Arkansas")))
                        :ARG2 (c4 / chief)))
            :ARG1 (q / quarterback)))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok denver -- a growing number of people are raiding their retirement plans to keep their homes , which is a huge mistake , warned personal finance expert <unk> orman .
# ::alignments
(w / warn-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "orman")
            :ARG1-of (e / expert-01
                  :ARG2 (f / finance
                        :ARG1-of (p2 / personal-02))))
      :ARG1 (r / raid-01
            :ARG0 (p3 / person
                  :quant (n2 / number
                        :ARG1-of (g / grow-01)))
            :ARG1 (p4 / plan-01
                  :ARG0 p3
                  :ARG1 (r2 / retire-01
                        :ARG0 p3)
                  :ARG2 (k / keep-01
                        :ARG0 p3
                        :ARG1 (h / home
                              :poss p3)))
            :ARG1-of (m / mistake-02
                  :mod (h2 / huge))))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the opposition bharatiya janata party -lrb- bjp -rrb- will be going ahead with its plan to move a no-confidence motion against the eight-month-old united front government during the current budget session , the times of india said today .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (n / newspaper
            :name (n2 / name
                  :op1 "Times")
            :poss (c / country
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "India")))
      :ARG1 (g / go-06
            :ARG0 (p / political-party
                  :name (n4 / name
                        :op1 "Bharatiya"
                        :op2 "Jitata"
                        :op3 "Party")
                  :ARG0-of (o / oppose-01))
            :ARG1 (p2 / plan-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (m / move-02
                        :ARG0 p
                        :ARG1 (m2 / motion
                              :topic (c2 / confident-01
                                    :polarity -))
                        :prep-against (g2 / government-organization
                              :ARG0-of (g3 / govern-01)
                              :ARG1-of (u / unite-01)
                              :age (t / temporal-quantity
                                    :quant 8
                                    :unit (m3 / month)))
                        :time (s2 / session
                              :mod (b / budget)
                              :time (c3 / current))))
            :ARG2 (a / ahead))
      :time (t2 / today))

                              :mod (s / star))))

                  :op1 (t2 / temporal-quantity
                        :quant 6
                        :unit (w / week))
                  :part-of (s2 / season
                        :mod (l / league
                              :mod (f / football)
                              :mod (n3 / nation))))
            :ARG1-of (c / cause-01
                  :ARG0 (s3 / sprained-01
                        :ARG1 (a / ankle)))))

                        :mod (s3 / storm
                              :mod (t2 / tropical)))))
      :ARG2 (g2 / grow-02

# ::alignments
(h / hit-01
      :ARG0 (s / strike-02
            :mod (ii / indefinite)
            :ARG1-of (g / general-02)
            :ARG1-of (o / organize-01
                  :ARG0 (a / and
                        :op1 (f / forum
                              :purpose (r / right-05
                                    :ARG1 (p / person
                                          :mod (c / country-region
                                                :name (n / name
                                                      :op1 "Madhesi")))))
                        :op2 (p2 / political-party
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Nepal"
                                    :op2 "Sadbhavana"
                                    :op3 "Party"))
                        :op3 (p3 / political-party
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Illinois"
                                    :op2 "Democratic"
                                    :op3 "Party")))))
      :ARG1 (l / life)
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / thursday))
      :location (d2 / district
            :quant (s2 / some)
            :location (s3 / southeast
                  :part-of c
                  :name (n4 / name
                        :op1 "Nepal"
                        :op2 "Terai"
                        :op3 "Plains"))))

                        :ARG1-of (w / weight-01)

                              :ARG1-of (k / key-02)

# ::alignments
(k / kill-01
      :ARG0 (a / accident
            :mod (c / car)
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (s / saturday))
            :location (d2 / division
                  :mod c)
            :location (c2 / city
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Daudi"))
            :location (c3 / country-region
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Arusha")
                  :location (n3 / north
                        :part-of (c4 / country
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Tanzania")))))
      :ARG1 (p / person))

                                                      :mod (l / last)))
                                          :ARG0-of (d2 / destroy-01
                                                :ARG1 (a3 / and
                                                      :op1 (h2 / home)
                                                      :op2 (ii / infrastructure)
                                                      :op3 (f / farm)
                                                      :quant (m3 / multiple
                                                            :op1 1000)))))))))
      :location (h3 / here)
      :time (d3 / date-entity
            :weekday (t / tuesday)))
